com.ibm.watson.dsm.engine

Class TupleState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.watson.dsm.engine.TupleState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TupleState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Holds the values of all tuples in the engine. Tuples are grouped by their type: Input, Transient, Persistent or Transport. An instance (or instances) of this is captured using IRuleEngine.getTupleState() or AnalysisEngine.getEndStates().
    Author:
    dawood
    See Also:
